"name":"STRING","shape":6,"type":"STRING","links":null}],"properties":{"cnr_id":"comfyui-custom-scripts","ver":"f2838ed5e59de4d73cde5c98354b87a8d3200190","Node name for S&R":"ShowText|pysssss","ue_properties":{"widget_ue_connectable":{},"input_ue_unconnectable":{},"version":"7.5.2"}},"widgets_values":["【图像类别】cosplay类\n主体呈现一位身着白色洛丽塔风格连衣裙的少女，头戴饰有黑花与蝴蝶结的宽檐帽，银白色长发柔顺垂落。她双手捧着一本深红色封面的精装书阅读，书页微张，手指轻压封面边缘，姿态自然放松。裙摆带有多层荷叶边装饰，脚穿黑色长筒靴，腿部线条清晰可见。\n构图采用中心偏右布局，人物主体占据画面中下部约60%垂直空间，水平方向居中略偏右15%，形成视觉重心。背景左侧为木质书架与台灯，右侧为模糊的室内墙面，整体呈现对称式平衡结构，但通过人物姿态打破绝对对称，增强动态感。\n视角为近距平视拍摄，模拟观众坐在桌前观察的角度，镜头略有倾斜以贴合人物坐姿。景深较浅，焦点集中在人物面部与手中书本，背景书架与台灯呈柔和虚化，突出主体。光线来自左侧窗户，形成侧逆光效果，在发丝边缘勾勒金色轮廓光，同时照亮书页与裙摆褶皱。\n色彩以白、黑、红为主调，辅以暖黄窗光与冷灰阴影，整体色调柔和且具层次感。材质细节丰富：织物呈现细腻褶皱与光泽，皮肤质感光滑带微光，书本封面显陈旧纹理，玻璃灯罩反射清晰。氛围静谧温馨，充满沉浸式阅读体验的宁静感，符合cosplay类图像对角色还原度与场景真实性的要求。\n（字数：348）"]},{"id":113,"type":"ShowText|pysssss","pos":[-1270,2110],"size":[390,520],"flags":{},"order":23,"mode":4,"inputs":[{"localized_name":"文本","name":"text","type":"STRING","link":322}],"outputs":[{"label":"字符串","localized_name":"字符串","name":"STRING","shape":6,"type":"STRING","links":null}],"properties":{"cnr_id":"comfyui-custom-scripts","ver":"f2838ed5e59de4d73cde5c98354b87a8d3200190","Node name for S&R":"ShowText|pysssss","ue_properties":{"widget_ue_connectable":{},"input_ue_unconnectable":{},"version":"7.5.2"}},"widgets_values":[]},{"id":200,"type":"ShowText|pysssss","pos":[-1550,1270],"size":[530,540],"flags":{},"order":24,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"localized_name":"文本","name":"text","type":"STRING","link":312}],"outputs":[{"localized_name":"字符串","name":"STRING","shape":6,"type":"STRING","links":null}],"properties":{"cnr_id":"comfyui-custom-scripts","ver":"609f3afaa74b2f88ef9ce8d939626065e3247469","Node name for S&R":"ShowText|pysssss","ue_properties":{"widget_ue_connectable":{},"input_ue_unconnectable":{},"version":"7.8"}},"widgets_values":["杰作，最佳质量，高分辨率，8K，人像摄影，年轻女孩，长发，黑色直发，披肩而下，柔顺发丝，自然垂落，杏仁眼，清澈眼神，温柔微笑，甜美表情，白皙肌肤，细腻毛孔，健康肤色，自然光，窗边光线，柔和侧逆光，丁达尔效应，室内环境，木质地板，浅景深，大光圈，f/1.8，背景虚化，氛围感强，时尚穿搭，简约风格，半身像，肩部入镜，中近景，35mm镜头，胶片质感，颗粒细腻，高对比度，光影层次，情绪价值，清新自然，生活气息，真实感强，细节丰富，面部轮廓清晰，发丝光泽，皮肤纹理，温暖色调，低饱和度，宁静氛围，午后时光，独处时刻，优雅气质，青春活力，纯净无瑕，视觉享受"]},{"id":106,"type":"llama_cpp_parameters","pos":[-520,1520],"size":[390,370],"flags":{},"order":2,"mode":4,"inputs":[{"label":"最大token数","localized_name":"max_tokens","name":"max_tokens","type":"INT","widget":{"name":"max_tokens"},"link":null},{"label":"采样候选数","localized_name":"top_k","name":"top_k","type":"INT","widget":{"name":"top_k"},"link":null},{"label":"核心采样阈值","localized_name":"top_p","name":"top_p","type":"FLOAT","widget":{"name":"top_p"},"link":null},{"label":"最小采样概率","localized_name":"min_p","name":"min_p","type":"FLOAT","widget":{"name":"min_p"},"link":null},{"label":"典型采样阈值","localized_name":"typical_p","name":"typical_p","type":"FLOAT","widget":{"name":"typical_p"},"link":null},{"label":"生成温度","localized_name":"temperature","name":"temperature","type":"FLOAT","widget":{"name":"temperature"},"link":null},{"label":"重复惩罚","localized_name":"repeat_penalty","name":"repeat_penalty","type":"FLOAT","widget":{"name":"repeat_penalty"},"link":null},{"label":"频率惩罚","localized_name":"frequency_penalty","name":"frequency_penalty","type":"FLOAT","widget":{"name":"frequency_penalty"},"link":null},{"label":"存在惩罚","localized_name":"presence_penalty","name":"presence_penalty","type":"FLOAT","widget":{"name":"presence_penalty"},"link":null},{"label":"Mirostat模式","localized_name":"mirostat_mode","name":"mirostat_mode","type":"INT","widget":{"name":"mirostat_mode"},"link":null},{"label":"Mirostat学习率","localized_name":"mirostat_eta","name":"mirostat_eta","type":"FLOAT","widget":{"name":"mirostat_eta"},"link":null},{"label":"Mirostat目标困惑度","localized_name":"mirostat_tau","name":"mirostat_tau","type":"FLOAT","widget":{"name":"mirostat_tau"},"link":null},{"label":"对话状态ID","localized_name":"state_uid","name":"state_uid","type":"INT","widget":{"name":"state_uid"},"link":null},{"label":"推理预算","localized_name":"reasoning_budget","name":"reasoni